snippet.title: Paradigm Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer for Paradigm, a 2D, pixel-art, platforming, puzzle game were you clone yourself to progress through obstacles, Play for free now, on Itch.io. 

Itch.io game link: https://artindi.itch.io/paradigm

Follow me on Itch.io: https://artindi.itch.io/
Follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheArtindi
Join my discord if you want, sometimes I do stuff there: https://discord.gg/EHDTdkN

Contact: 
artindigames@gmail.com

Music: 
"Paradigm Trailer"
Written by me.
